FBIS4-68128 "jptot020__l94050" JPRS-TOT-94-020-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 12 May 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA LEBANON Amal Movement Issues Statement After Member Killed at Home Amal Movement Issues Statement After Member Killed at Home NC1205083094 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 0800 GMT 12 May 94 NC1205083094 Beirut Radio Lebanon Arabic BFN [Text] 'Abd-al-Rahman Sulayman was killed at his home in al- 'Amiriyah, south of Tyre, at about 0215 today. Unidentified people planted an explosive device near his house. The explosion killed Sulayman immediately and wounded his brother. The Amal Movement has issued a statement on Sulayman's murder, pledging to press ahead on the path of resistance until the land is liberated.
